question:
Background: There are 4 types of District: Heritage District, Entertainment District, Wall Street, and Restaurant District.
There are 4 types of Supermarkets: Weis Markets, Costco, Tesco, and Auchan.
There are 4 types of Product: Canned Sauces, Buns, Cookies, and Canned Coconut Milk.
There are 4 types of Ingredient: Lard, Couscous, Barbecue Sauce, and Sesame Oil.
Each Heritage District has Auchan, Tesco, and Weis Markets.
Each Entertainment District has Weis Markets.
Each Wall Street has Tesco.
Each Restaurant District has Weis Markets.
Each Weis Markets has Buns.
Each Costco has Canned Sauces.
Each Tesco has Buns, Canned Coconut Milk, and Cookies.
Each Auchan has Canned Coconut Milk.
Each Canned Sauces has Barbecue Sauce.
Each Buns has Lard and Barbecue Sauce.
Each Cookies has Lard.
Each Canned Coconut Milk has Sesame Oil and Couscous.
The number of each Buns 's Barbecue Sauce equals 19.
The number of each Wall Street 's Tesco equals 18.
The number of each Tesco 's Canned Coconut Milk equals each Wall Street 's Tesco.
The number of each Buns 's Lard equals 13.
The number of each Entertainment District 's Weis Markets equals each Weis Markets 's Buns.
The number of each Cookies 's Lard equals the difference of each Wall Street 's Supermarkets and each Wall Street 's Tesco.
The number of each Canned Coconut Milk 's Sesame Oil equals 19 times each Restaurant District 's Weis Markets.
The number of each Weis Markets 's Buns equals 6 times the sum of each Canned Sauces 's Barbecue Sauce, each Restaurant District 's Weis Markets, and each Canned Coconut Milk 's Sesame Oil.
The number of each Tesco 's Cookies equals 3 times the difference of each Restaurant District 's Weis Markets and each Costco 's Canned Sauces.
The number of each Tesco 's Buns equals 8 times each Heritage District 's Tesco.
The number of each Costco 's Canned Sauces equals 13.
The number of each Canned Coconut Milk 's Couscous equals each Canned Sauces 's Barbecue Sauce.
The number of each Heritage District 's Weis Markets equals 6 times the difference of each Canned Sauces 's Barbecue Sauce and each Entertainment District 's Weis Markets.
The number of each Restaurant District 's Weis Markets equals 20.
The number of each Heritage District 's Tesco equals 9 more than the difference of each Entertainment District 's Weis Markets and each Weis Markets 's Buns.
The number of each Auchan 's Canned Coconut Milk equals 22 times each Wall Street 's Supermarkets.
The number of each Heritage District 's Auchan equals the sum of each Restaurant District 's Supermarkets, each Costco 's Product, each Heritage District 's Tesco, and each Buns 's Barbecue Sauce.
The number of each Canned Sauces 's Barbecue Sauce equals each Restaurant District 's Weis Markets.
How many Tesco does Wall Street have?
solution: Define each Wall Street 's Tesco as H; So H = 18.
